Catalog
contains all departments: centralized object for information (at the price of constant embedded accesses), will be important for course lookup when implementing prereqs specs in the future
CatalogDriver
Driver class for the CatalogParser package.
CatalogDriver.AllListener
AllListener is the listener for the button that launches a catalog with both Undergrad and Graduate courses.
CatalogDriver.GradListener
GradListener is a listener for the button that selects the Gradeuate catalog to be launched.
CatalogDriver.UGListener
UGListener is a listener for the button that selects the Undergraduate catalog to be launched.
CatalogPanel
Main panel that contains all the catalog information, launched in CatalogDriver.
Course
Course Object stores information of a particular course.
Department
Department Object contains a list for all the Courses in a particular Department.
Restriction
Restriction is a class that stores static strings of common course restrictions.
